Laltu... Punjab.
India!

00:13:10.680 --> 00:13:14.260
Kode pos 141021!

00:13:14.850 --> 00:13:16.050
Dasar sampah!

00:13:29.850 --> 00:13:31.890
Kapan Hardy sampai Dubai?

