- Oke?
- Oke.

00:19:23.730 --> 00:19:26.560
Nyonya, carilah pelatih gulat.

00:19:26.680 --> 00:19:27.930
Pelajari beberapa gerakan.

00:19:28.560 --> 00:19:30.980
Jangan terlihat tidak
tahu dasar-dasar gulat.

00:19:33.520 --> 00:19:35.400
Harus cari kemana aku?

